\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
(Optional) Tin the SHV jack end of the tube in the same manner the SHV jack
 was tinned.
 Check the fit again, if it doesn't go in there's probably a solder blob
 that needs to be wicked away.
